Borg Says Mechanism for Recapitalizing Banks ‘Very Important’

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-04T07:13:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/borg-says-mechanism-for-recapitalizing-banks-very-important-.html
Swedish Finance Minister Anders Borg
said it is “very important” to have a mechanism for
recapitalizing banks in order to combat the debt crisis.  “The most important thing is to build firewalls and to get
the backstops in place,” Borg told reporters in Luxembourg
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
